Subject: [PATCH 063/609] ARM: omap: am335x evm: Add support for RTC

Original commit: 290719922225a9c2cad7e5ced72f4458efad5566

  From git://arago-project.org/git/projects/linux-am33x.git
  And ti-sdk-am335x-evm-05.05.00.00-Linux-x86-Install image

